{"tid":2447626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"制止浪費 提醒顧客勿過量點餐 北京擬規定食肆設勸導員","createTime":"2021-03-15T10:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:02:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05e56219c64986cc68f75f96f8c667c4b531a3b8","tid":2447626,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"制止浪費 提醒顧客勿過量點餐 北京擬規定食肆設勸導員<br />\n<br />\n原文請按： <a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/255515/?utm_campaign=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F255515%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dcopy&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=816e488e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/255515/?utm_campaign=copy</a><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平去年8月提出要堅決制止餐飲浪費後，全國人大隨即草擬《反食品浪費法》並提請常委會審議，各省市人大亦陸續跟進立法。北京市人大常委會上周五開會，審議《北京市反食品浪費規定(草案)》，當中規定，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">任何人都有權勸阻、舉報浪費行為，食肆更要設立勸導員，提醒顧客適量點餐、取餐及打包剩餘食品，對明顯過量點餐、取餐的行為作出提醒、勸導。 <br />\n<br />\n  《草案》除了提出要食肆設勸導員，還提出食肆應對「光盤」消費者給予獎勵或優惠，並要在菜單上標明菜式主要材料、分量、建議食用人數等資料，以及明示服務項目和收費標準，不得設定不公平、不合理交易條件，誘導、誤導消費者超量點餐。《草案》又為自助餐業者就客人浪費食物額外收費「撐腰」，指業者可在事先說明後，對造成浪費的客人收取相應費用。 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，《草案》鼓勵超市、商場、便利店等食品經營者，對預先包裝並臨近保質期的食品，設專區集中陳列出售，避免浪費，同時鼓勵向公益慈善組織、福利救助機構等捐贈保質期內可安全食用的食品，而若捐贈的食品臨近保質期，應在當眼處標明並通知對方。 <br />\n<br />\n至於最為人詬病的「吃播」，《草案》提出，網絡音頻視頻信息服務提供者應加強相關信息審核，一旦發現製作、發布、傳播宣揚「量大多吃」、「暴飲暴食」等浪費食物的內容，應及時制止並停止傳輸，情況嚴重時更應立即停止提供服務，若業者未履行審核義務或製作、發布、傳播宣揚浪費食物的內容，由網絡信息管理部門依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往： <a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/255515/?utm_campaign=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F255515%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dcopy&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=816e488e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/255515/?utm_campaign=copy</a>"},{"pid":"d2832ee87f57d2e38813dbf44e8af698e1362875","tid":2447626,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"又有新職位可以gdp gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3aa3ca7bab9cc01f705a30383248ef4866d7b3","tid":2447626,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"點菜司？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0888b6d5098440a9108f43c79784242432f4ba75","tid":2447626,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:10:21.000Z","msg":"一係由n-1變n-n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32ec3849ca768db18829523e9a1ecfb8d54d6a5","tid":2447626,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:10:38.000Z","msg":"點菜師先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9f6db51f48c9872a38ee28c8627f01b98bee2a","tid":2447626,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:11:59.000Z","msg":"食蟹唔食殼,算唔算浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b665b407ceb93a4dec05f95911627eaedcae76","tid":2447626,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"人民鬥人民"},{"pid":"b1a11f6e87b5f658a7946b6e936fcccfe894ccc5","tid":2447626,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"營養師"},{"pid":"03e6bc646405288d34a2bdb6fa138a7e699ae852","tid":2447626,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01bbd1e4852f4ad097149b4caea74d1c